org.gitlab.api

Class GitlabMergeRequest.Query

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gitlab.api.GitlabMergeRequest.Query
  • Enclosing class:
    GitlabMergeRequest

    public static class GitlabMergeRequest.Query
extends java.lang.Object
    This extends GitlabQuery and supports query global GitlabMergeRequests with searching scope and range. Build this query with setters and call query() to execute query.

    Gitlab Web API: https://docs.gitlab.com/ee/api/merge_requests.html#list-merge-requests

    GET /merge_requests
